Class OsmAgentBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.liris.smartgov.simulator.core.agent.core.AgentBody<MoverAction>

  • public class OsmAgentBody
extends GeoAgentBody
    An agent body moving in the OSM graph, as in a vehicle. This agent can move between OsmNodes on OsmArcs using the CarMover.
